# Watchlist API Test

### Get watchlist (IDs only)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/watchlist
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

### Get watchlist with products (page 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/watchlist/products?page=1&limit=8
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

### Add product to watchlist
POST http://localhost:3000/api/watchlist/add/1
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

### Remove product from watchlist
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/watchlist/remove/1
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

### Check if product is in watchlist
GET http://localhost:3000/api/watchlist/check/1
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE
